<plot>The emigrants are absolute protagonists of this documentary where there is no room for anything that was not their voices. The testimony follows one past another in a continuous and constant flow that unites and at the same time divides the stories. A document to be taken all at once breath, that leaves time to think only on the faces of men, icons of their time.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?176433</url></doc>
